apa kau merasa ada yang aneh
dari Sanshang?

504
00:32:11,290 --> 00:32:11,860
Kenapa?

505
00:32:13,150 --> 00:32:14,030
Entahlah.

506
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:16,790
Hanya merasa aneh.

507
00:32:18,870 --> 00:32:20,450
Terutama senyumnya itu.

508
00:32:21,900 --> 00:32:24,100
Setelah kau bilang, aku juga
merasa ada sedikit.

509
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:28,640
Bagaimanapun, dia baru kehilangan ayahnya,

510
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:31,540
pasti memerlukan waktu untuk
menyesuaikan diri.

511
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:46,630
Aktris populer, Kak Xun,

512
00:32:46,690 --> 00:32:48,310
berkencan di hotel dengan
pria misterius,

513
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:49,650
terlihat akrab dan mesra,

514
00:32:49,650 --> 00:32:51,240
diduga hubungan rahasianya ketahuan.

515
00:32:51,710 --> 00:32:52,290
Coba kulihat.

516
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:00,030
Apa kalian ada merasa...

517
00:33:00,570 --> 00:33:02,760
pria ini sedikit mirip Pak Sun?

518
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:03,950
Pak Sun?

519
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:07,360
Pak Sun dan Kak Xun

520
00:33:07,360 --> 00:33:08,910
bukan orang dari dunia yang sama.

521
00:33:12,330 --> 00:33:14,270
Sanshang pasti ada masalah.

522
00:33:20,040 --> 00:33:21,040
Astaga!

523
00:33:21,950 --> 00:33:23,810
Kak Xun dan kekasihnya sudah ketahuan.

524
00:33:24,030 --> 00:33:25,180
Siapa yang ketahuan?

525
00:33:25,650 --> 00:33:27,140
Kekasihnya Kak Xun.

526
00:33:27,460 --> 00:33:28,220
Kekasih siapa?

527
00:33:28,490 --> 00:33:29,220
Kak Xun.

528
00:33:29,430 --> 00:33:30,140
Siapa itu Kak Xun?

529
00:33:30,210 --> 00:33:31,330
Kau cepat lihat Weibo.

530
00:33:31,620 --> 00:33:32,350
Apa itu Weibo?

531
00:33:34,260 --> 00:33:34,830
Pergi kau!

532
00:33:35,430 --> 00:33:36,380
Dasar otak tersumbat.

533
00:33:36,380 --> 00:33:37,800
(Qiyi; Du Ang)

534
00:33:37,800 --> 00:33:40,700
(Apa kau besok ada waktu luang?)

535
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:44,500
(Apa yang kau lakukan besok?)

536
00:33:45,420 --> 00:33:45,940
(Senyum)

537
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:59,799
(Ada apa?)

538
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:03,820
(Besok hari ulang tahunku.)

539
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:10,860
(Bagaimana merayakannya?)

540
00:34:12,820 --> 00:34:15,340
(Makan, minum, bermain,
apa kau ada waktu?)

541
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:18,020
(Ada.)

542
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:23,500
(Bar Laocun)

543
00:34:42,980 --> 00:34:43,350
Du Ang,

544
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:44,340
selamat ulang tahun.

545
00:34:49,090 --> 00:34:49,650
Qiyi,

546
00:34:51,340 --> 00:34:52,570
suasana hatiku sekarang...

547
00:34:54,010 --> 00:34:55,260
sama seperti bunga mawar ini.

548
00:34:57,890 --> 00:34:58,740
Apa yang sedang kau lakukan?

549
00:34:59,690 --> 00:35:00,170
Aku...

550
00:35:01,420 --> 00:35:02,770
Tidak cukup setia kawan, ya, Bro,

551
00:35:02,890 --> 00:35:04,470
ulang tahun juga tidak beritahu aku.

552
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,430
Ayo, kita pergi makan.

553
00:35:06,750 --> 00:35:07,240
Bukan,

554
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:09,230
kenapa kalian ke sini?

555
00:35:10,890 --> 00:35:11,730
Kalau begitu, kami tidak datang,

556
00:35:11,990 --> 00:35:12,930
Qiyi, ayo.

557
00:35:13,220 --> 00:35:13,640
Ayo, ayo, ayo.

558
00:35:13,640 --> 00:35:14,200
Sebentar, sebentar.

559
00:35:16,610 --> 00:35:18,230
Kita sama-sama pergi makan saja.

560
00:35:18,690 --> 00:35:19,260
Memohonlah padaku.

561
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:27,310
Aku mohon, Kak Kaixin.

562
00:35:29,180 --> 00:35:29,980
Begini masih lumayan,

563
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:30,330
ayo.

564
00:35:30,410 --> 00:35:30,740
Ayo.

565
00:35:40,680 --> 00:35:41,540
Namun, aku...

566
00:35:42,930 --> 00:35:44,130
aku tidak memiliki air mata.

567
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:46,460
Semesta...

568
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:48,810
semesta juga tidak memiliki air mata.

569
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:50,810
Apa gunanya air mata?

570
00:35:53,090 --> 00:35:54,550
Kita hanya memiliki badai,

571
00:35:54,610 --> 00:35:56,650
hanya petir, hanya kilat.

572
00:35:56,910 --> 00:35:58,890
Kami tidak memiliki hujan
yang merepotkan.

573
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:01,320
Ini adalah tekadku.

574
00:36:01,940 --> 00:36:03,280
Tekad alam semesta!

575
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:06,110
Menderulah, angin.

576
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:07,870
Bergemuruhlah, petir.

577
00:36:08,030 --> 00:36:09,350
Berkelebatlah, kilat.

578
00:36:09,830 --> 00:36:12,310
Buat semua makhluk yang tertidur
dalam kegelapan ini

579
00:36:12,550 --> 00:36:13,590
menjadi musnah!

580
00:36:13,820 --> 00:36:14,820
Musnah!

581
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:24,300
(Yuan Lang)

582
00:36:25,570 --> 00:36:26,190
Qiyi,

583
00:36:26,550 --> 00:36:26,970
duduklah.

584
00:36:33,020 --> 00:36:33,630
Terima kasih.

585
00:36:37,370 --> 00:36:38,360
Aku duduk di sini.

586
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:39,740
Minggir.

587
00:36:41,870 --> 00:36:42,380
Qiyi,

588
00:36:42,930 --> 00:36:43,910
mau makan apa pesan saja.

589
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,490
Ruang Paviliun, dua orang.

590
00:36:46,750 --> 00:36:47,740
Tetap pesan yang biasa.

591
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:48,610
Baik.

592
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:59,630
Aku mau makan
"Kelahiranku Pasti Bermakna".

593
00:37:00,590 --> 00:37:02,900
Kau lebih cocok makan
"Keindahan Bunga Taman Tidak Tertutupi".

594
00:37:04,970 --> 00:37:06,460
Apa kau sedang bilang aku cantik?

595
00:37:07,570 --> 00:37:08,720
"Angsa Senja di Pohon Tua".

596
00:37:11,220 --> 00:37:12,460
Qiyi, pesanlah.

597
00:37:15,910 --> 00:37:17,470
Inilah tempat yang sering kau datangi?

598
00:37:18,430 --> 00:37:20,060
Aku selalu ingin mengundangmu
datang duduk dan mengobrol.

599
00:37:20,970 --> 00:37:21,550
Qiyi.

600
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:23,580
Terima kasih.

601
00:37:27,410 --> 00:37:28,410
Siapa...

602
00:37:29,180 --> 00:37:30,610
sampai membawa pengawal?

603
00:37:31,030 --> 00:37:31,500
Siapa?

604
00:37:31,910 --> 00:37:32,790
Siapa yang bawa pengawal?

605
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:11,500
♪Aku menyimpan semua perasaanku
Di dalam hati♪

606
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:17,220
♪Tidak berani mengungkapkan jejak cinta♪

607
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:26,140
♪Aku selalu kurang pengetahuan
Tentang cinta♪

608
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:31,830
♪Belum pernah bertemu dengan
Denyut dunia♪

609
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:38,230
♪Kalau lebih dekat sedikit♪

610
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:41,410
♪Kali ini hati akan tergerak♪

611
00:38:41,410 --> 00:38:45,200
♪Walau terakhir kalinya♪

612
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:52,140
♪Membuktikan kalau aku berani
Menggandeng tanganmu♪

613
00:38:52,990 --> 00:38:57,360
♪Melihat tengah panggung
Kita akan mekar♪

614
00:38:57,360 --> 00:39:01,220
♪Langkah adalah impian dari cinta♪

615
00:39:01,220 --> 00:39:07,750
♪Setiap nada dan tempo
Ada karena keberadaanmu♪

616
00:39:07,750 --> 00:39:12,220
♪Dengar, setiap saat adalah kau dan aku♪

617
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:16,050
♪Menyanyikan lagu terindah bersama♪

618
00:39:16,050 --> 00:39:20,510
♪Akan selalu dikenang seumur hidup♪

619
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:25,680
♪Rasa haru yang tidak akan memudar♪

620
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:34,600
♪Rasa haru yang tidak akan
Memudar seumur hidup♪

